pydocstring.vim
===============

Pydocstring is a generater of Python docstring.

 * Insert one-line docstring.
 * Insert multi-line docstring.
 * Insert comment.

This plugin is heavily inspired by phpdoc.vim and sonictemplate.vim.
- phpdoc.vim
  http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1355
- sonictemplate.vim
  https://github.com/mattn/sonictemplate-vim


Usage
  1. Move cursor on `def`, `class` keyword line.
  2. Type :Pydocstring or <C-l> which is default key mapping to insert docstring.
  3. Insert docstring under the `def`, `class` keyword line.
